---
title: Dilly Chickpea & Cucumber Grain Bowls with Feta, Creamy Red Pepper Hummus & Almonds
description: Get ready to love this delicious, vegetarian 10-minute lunch idea: You’ll start with a bowl of whole grains like bulgur, rice, and barley, then mix in earthy marinated chickpeas, lemon zest, fresh dill, crunchy almonds, and refreshing cukes. Add salty crumbled feta on top, then dollop it all with creamy red pepper hummus and finish with a squeeze of lemon juice before digging in. Don’t be fooled by its wholesome vegetarian title—trust us, this meal is a massive flavor bomb!
